#

Beef Tenderloin Sandwich with Horseradish Sauce

25 min
$15
600 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 1

Allergens:

Gluten

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Cuisine:

American

Course:

LunchDinner

Tags:

SandwichQuick MealBeef

Description

A deliciously tender beef sandwich topped with a zesty horseradish sauce, perfect for a quick lunch or dinner.

Ingredients

  • beef tenderloin: 8 oz
  • baguette or ciabatta bread: 1 piece
  • horseradish sauce: 2 tbsp
  • arugula or spinach: 1 handful
  • olive oil: 1 tbsp
  • salt and pepper: to taste
